    Hicham is situated in the Gueliz district of Marrakech, and is 2 km from Marrakech Parking Koutoubia. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and a concierge service, along with free WiFi. The property …
    Hicham is situated in the Gueliz district of Marrakech, and is 2 km from Marrakech Parking Koutoubia. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and a concierge service, along with free WiFi. The property is close to popular attractions like Carré Eden Shopping Center, Marrakech Plaza and Conference Palace.
    All units in the hotel are equipped with a flat-screen TV.
    A buffet breakfast can be enjoyed at the property.
    Hicham offers an outdoor pool.
    Acima Massira Marrakech is 4.3 km from the accommodation, while Conference Palace is 1.2 km from the property. The nearest airport is Marrakech-Menara Airport, 4 km from Hicham.

    Gueliz

    The wide, French-era streets of Gueliz are home to upscale Moroccan and European restaurants, cabarets and chic bars, as well as art galleries and mainstream fashion stores. Created by the eponymous painter, and later owned by Yves Saint Laurent, the Majorelle Garden has grasses, cactuses, flowers and various elements painted cobalt blue. Near El-Harti Park, the Church of the Holy Martyrs has Moorish-style arches.
